[I] OBS Studio filter for applying an arbitrary shader to a source

[T] The obs-shaderfilter plugin for OBS Studio is intended to allow users to
[T] apply their own shaders to OBS sources. This theoretically makes possible
[T] some simple effects like drop shadows that can be implemented strictly in
[T] shader code.

